comments.body: Move the email notification to its own ticket: https://github.com/pulibrary/tiger-data-app/issues/195

The code to fetch records sponsored by the current user was added on https://github.com/pulibrary/tiger-data-app/pull/190, but I forgot to tag this issue. The relevant piece of code is in the Project model:

```
def self.sponsored_projects(sponsor)
    Project.where("metadata_json->>'data_sponsor' = ?", sponsor)
  end
```
